{"tid":698312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個良好搭的士經驗","createTime":"2018-06-11T14:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T02:45:35.000Z","uid":75998,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"27900803b54af0d3fbd0acd34d29d02f35e6fc88","tid":698312,"uid":75998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:35:36.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n後生仔揸 個名兩個字嘅（同幾好聽） 架車幾香 無嗰啲作嘔嘅味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n駕駛態度安全良好 唔會一路㩒電話號一路揸車 無推人閘人<br />\n<br />\n收錢嗰陣四捨五都捨 畀大紙試下佢 佢又真係找返毫子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果香港多啲哩啲司機就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8871a816c34c19379a742b9938fcd138608de7a4","tid":698312,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"去錯地方又趕住比賽<br />\n石硤尾過海去中山體育館<br />\n<br />\n落車發現唔夠錢 我話比身份證佢 之後比錢拎返<br />\n佢話算啦 有幾多你比幾多啦 <br />\n比左$140 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8220c69b2199a461bc14eec86423ed67d699e7ec","tid":698312,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:38:54.000Z","msg":"司機唔收我錢"},{"pid":"2d564c211178828b26a80f1cec53309742e9ee39","tid":698312,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"this is gay"},{"pid":"cf2160481267a6ca25cf4de84f7689ae28fd206b","tid":698312,"uid":173286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:53:00.000Z","msg":"無。"},{"pid":"fadf03e5898698ff592b771254b0900ef6c39f44","tid":698312,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:54:37.000Z","msg":"車費肉償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ba468ef3a87aa67d5513049bb8a18cec466179","tid":698312,"uid":75998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8871a816c34c19379a742b9938fcd138608de7a4","tid":698312,"uid":23815,"like":0,